  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0 \u0da2\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9d\u0dcf\u0dad\u0db1\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Murders a millionaire woman who lived alone",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Mahanuwara headquarters police say that a 65-year-old millionaire woman who lived alone in a large house in Lake Circle, Kandy, was hacked to death.",
        "The police say that the murder took place today (14) around 02 in the afternoon. The police also say that a woman named Kamani Ranasinghe (65) was killed.",
        "According to the police, the woman had rented a large number of shops near the large house where she had retired from an executive grade job in the government and lived alone in the house. Police investigations revealed that the woman's husband had died earlier and their two children were living in Australia.",
        "An eyewitness who did not wish to be named said that at around 2pm yesterday (14th) he saw a black man about five feet tall come out of the house where the woman lived with a knife and his hand was cut and bleeding.",
        "The spokesman said that he did not go near him because the man threatened him with a knife and later went inside the house and said that the deceased woman was lying on the ground and struggling. He said that since she died shortly after that, he did not take steps to hospitalize her and he said that he informed the police about it.",
        "The police suspect that the murder took place over a property issue and further police investigation is being carried out through several stages."
      ],
